               <p>I saw this hemp before the Justice, in the possession of the prisoner John Brown.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to by the Prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17861025-89-person1175">
                  WILLIAM
                   CLARKE
               <interp inst="t17861025-89-person1175" type="surname" value="CLARKE"></interp>
